metadata.fieldPath: root.Config Version.Config Version
metadata.tooltip:
The plugin version number. This is set by the developer and should not be edited. Format: Major.Minor.Patch (e.g., 2.0.31)

Examples: 2.0.31, 1.5.0

metadata.fieldPath: root.Configuration Options.Configuration Options.Armor damage (PVE).Armor damage (PVE)
metadata.tooltip:
Controls player vs player combat.
TruePVE typically disables PvP in certain areas or times.

Examples: true, false

Examples: 0, 13076, 10135

metadata.fieldPath: root.Configuration Options.Configuration Options.Reflect PVP Damage Multipliers (0 = disabled, 1 = 100%).Reflect PVP Damage Multipliers (0 = disabled, 1 = 100%).Multiplier Allows Armor Protection.Multiplier Allows Armor Protection
metadata.tooltip:
A multiplier that affects rates, speeds, or amounts. • 1.0 = normal (100%, no change)
• 2.0 = double (200%, 2x effect)
• 0.5 = half (50%, 0.5x effect)

Used for gathering rates, craft speeds, etc.

Examples: 0.5, 1.0, 2.0, 5.0
